T02TD3191E:201a-4: lte yul steng du legs gsal ba'i //
T02TD3191E:201a-5: chos 'byung dmar po'i nang du ni //
T02TD3191E:201a-6: rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa //
T02TD3191E:201a-7: lte bar gzi brjid 'od mchog can //
T02TD3191E:201a-8: yi ge h'um dkar sgras bskyed pa //
T02TD3191E:201a-9: mtshog ma'i mtshams su nges 'byung ba'i //
T02TD3191E:201a-10: h'um yig dud khas legs bskyed pa //
T02TD3191E:201a-11: nam mkha' khyab par blta bya ba //
T02TD3191E:201a-14: aa bha ya ka ra'i zhal snga nas tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
